definition: Chenxi county in Huaihua 懷化|怀化[Huai2 hua4], Hunan
5th earthly branch: 7-9 a.m., 3rd solar month (5th April-4th May), year of the Dragon/ancient Chinese compass point: 120°

sentences.english: From Chenxi County, like to play bamboo flute and cucurbit flute.
sentences.chinese: 來自辰溪縣，愛好笛子和葫蘆絲演奏。

sentences.english: Rectorite is discovered in the pelitic material of one of rock crystal deposit in the north-west of Chenxi county.
sentences.chinese: 累託石發現於辰溪縣西北部一個水晶礦牀的泥質物中。
